Package Assignment1

Class MyHealthData

java.lang.Object
Assignment1.MyHealthDataBase
Assignment1.MyHealthData
public class MyHealthData extends MyHealthDataBase
This class is named MyHealthData which extends MyHealthDataBase that includes method to calculate the Body Max Index (BMI). This class contains important health information about a patient (first and last name, gender, birth year, height, and weight) and demonstrates methods to calculate health metrics and display all patient's health data.
